---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import StructuredData from '../components/StructuredData.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Services | Start & Scale Growth Advisory"
	description="Revenue strategy, operations, fundraising prep, and AI advisory. Built from 15+ years of operating experience inside high-growth, founder-led companies."
	canonical="/services"
>
	<StructuredData type="organization" />

	<!-- Hero -->
			<section class="bg-dark pt-32 pb-16 sm:pt-40 sm:pb-20 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-28">
				<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
					<h1 class="font-display text-white text-h1 lg:text-[3.75rem] lg:leading-[1.05] max-w-4xl">
						Four ways we work with founders.
					</h1>
					<p class="text-body-lg text-body-light mt-6 max-w-2xl">
						Each one built from operating experience inside companies at every stage from stealth to IPO. In rooms where the playbook didn't exist yet.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Revenue & GTM -->
			<section id="revenue-gtm" class="bg-background py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
				<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
					<div class="max-w-3xl">
						<p class="text-small text-accent uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">01</p>
						<h2 class="font-display text-headline text-h2 lg:text-[3rem] lg:leading-[1.1]">Revenue & GTM</h2>
						<p class="text-body-lg text-body mt-6">
							Your product has traction but sales can't keep pace. Pipeline is inconsistent, reps are missing quota, and pricing was set eighteen months ago on a hunch.
						</p>
						<h3 class="font-display text-headline text-h4 mt-10">What we do</h3>
						<p class="text-body text-body mt-3">
							We design sales processes, build pipeline architecture, fix pricing, and structure your channel strategy. If you need to hire reps, we help you find the right ones and coach them through ramp.
						</p>
						<div class="bg-surface p-6 rounded mt-8">
							<p class="text-small text-accent uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Our track record</p>
							<p class="text-body text-body">
								Our team built the CloudKitchens Northeast revenue org from zero: 42 people, 9 markets, 8 months, 120%+ of plan. At WeWork, we scaled regional ARR from $20M to $120M in 24 months across 21 locations.
							</p>
						</div>
						<a href="https://calendly.com/chris-ssgrowthadvisors/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent text-btn mt-8 inline-block hover:text-accent-hover transition-colors duration-150 cursor-pointer">
							Talk about your revenue engine &rarr;
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Divider -->
			<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8"><hr class="border-border" /></div>

			<!-- Operations & Systems -->
			<section id="operations-systems" class="bg-background py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
				<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
					<div class="max-w-3xl">
						<p class="text-small text-accent uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">02</p>
						<h2 class="font-display text-headline text-h2 lg:text-[3rem] lg:leading-[1.1]">Operations & Systems</h2>
						<p class="text-body-lg text-body mt-6">
							Your team doubled but your processes didn't. The CRM is half-populated, marketing tools don't talk to each other, and pulling a report takes half a day.
						</p>
						<h3 class="font-display text-headline text-h4 mt-10">What we do</h3>
						<p class="text-body text-body mt-3">
							We implement and configure CRM (Salesforce, HubSpot), set up marketing automation, design repeatable processes, and build the data infrastructure that lets you see what's happening. We do the configuration ourselves.
						</p>
						<div class="bg-surface p-6 rounded mt-8">
							<p class="text-small text-accent uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Our track record</p>
							<p class="text-body text-body">
								We built a Salesforce NPSP instance for a national nonprofit operating across 29 states, then integrated it with Salesforce Marketing Cloud, GA4, and Givebutter for end-to-end donor tracking and digital fundraising.
							</p>
						</div>
						<a href="https://calendly.com/chris-ssgrowthadvisors/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent text-btn mt-8 inline-block hover:text-accent-hover transition-colors duration-150 cursor-pointer">
							Talk about your ops &rarr;
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Divider -->
			<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8"><hr class="border-border" /></div>

			<!-- Fundraising & Investor Readiness -->
			<section id="fundraising" class="bg-background py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
				<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
					<div class="max-w-3xl">
						<p class="text-small text-accent uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">03</p>
						<h2 class="font-display text-headline text-h2 lg:text-[3rem] lg:leading-[1.1]">Fundraising & Investor Readiness</h2>
						<p class="text-body-lg text-body mt-6">
							You need to raise but your story doesn't land. Metrics are in five different spreadsheets, your deck gets polite nods but no term sheets, and you're guessing at what investors want to see.
						</p>
						<h3 class="font-display text-headline text-h4 mt-10">What we do</h3>
						<p class="text-body text-body mt-3">
							We develop your deck, frame your narrative around what investors actually evaluate, package your metrics clearly, and build your outreach strategy. The work is informed by direct experience inside companies preparing to raise.
						</p>
						<div class="bg-surface p-6 rounded mt-8">
							<p class="text-small text-accent uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Our track record</p>
							<p class="text-body text-body">
								Our team has operated inside companies at every funding stage. Stealth launch at Allwhere (built GTM, generated 50% of revenue in 6 months). Rapid scale at WeWork through the IPO run. And the restructuring that followed.
							</p>
						</div>
						<a href="https://calendly.com/chris-ssgrowthadvisors/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent text-btn mt-8 inline-block hover:text-accent-hover transition-colors duration-150 cursor-pointer">
							Talk about your raise &rarr;
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Divider -->
			<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8"><hr class="border-border" /></div>

			<!-- AI & Automation Advisory -->
			<section id="ai-automation" class="bg-background py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
				<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
					<div class="max-w-3xl">
						<p class="text-small text-accent uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">04</p>
						<h2 class="font-display text-headline text-h2 lg:text-[3rem] lg:leading-[1.1]">AI & Automation Advisory</h2>
						<p class="text-body-lg text-body mt-6">
							You keep hearing you need AI. Maybe you've tried a few tools and nothing stuck, or you automated the wrong things, or you're not sure where to start.
						</p>
						<h3 class="font-display text-headline text-h4 mt-10">What we do</h3>
						<p class="text-body text-body mt-3">
							We run feasibility analysis on your workflows, select the right tools, build the implementation roadmap, and design agentic systems. We build these systems ourselves. When we recommend something, we can ship it.
						</p>
						<div class="bg-surface p-6 rounded mt-8">
							<p class="text-small text-accent uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Our track record</p>
							<p class="text-body text-body">
								We built a full-stack SaaS platform from zero: React, TypeScript, Supabase, 19 Edge Functions, AI document processing. Deployed and running in production. We also configure marketing automation, CRM integrations, and analytics pipelines.
							</p>
						</div>
						<a href="https://calendly.com/chris-ssgrowthadvisors/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent text-btn mt-8 inline-block hover:text-accent-hover transition-colors duration-150 cursor-pointer">
							Talk about AI for your business &rarr;
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- CTA Block -->
			<section class="bg-dark py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24">
				<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 text-center">
					<h2 class="font-display text-white text-h2 lg:text-[3rem] lg:leading-[1.1]">Not sure which applies?</h2>
					<p class="text-body-lg text-body-light mt-4 max-w-xl mx-auto">Most clients need a combination. Start with a 30-minute call and we'll figure out where the biggest bottleneck is.</p>
					<div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 items-center">
						<a href="https://calendly.com/chris-ssgrowthadvisors/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-accent text-white text-btn px-7 py-3.5 rounded hover:bg-accent-hover transition-colors duration-150 cursor-pointer inline-block">
							Book a Call
						</a>
						<a href="/contact" class="text-body-light text-btn hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150 cursor-pointer inline-block py-3.5">
							Or send a message &rarr;
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
</BaseLayout>
